pmacct (Promiscuous mode IP Accounting package)
pmacct is Copyright (C) 2003-2009 by Paolo Lucente

 + Continue the integration trend just started with BGP;
   by either remaining in the same area (routing protocols)
   or by addressing other topical areas.
 + Improvements to the plugins architecture; it would be
   great if one day, people could write plugins in other
   languages than C/C++. 
 + A never-ending task: find and evaluate appealing traffic
   collection methods and backends to implement.
